# Google OAuth client ID for the "Export to Google Drive" feature.
# Leave blank to disable Drive export (CSV + printable PDF still work).
#
# How to get one:
#   1. Go to https://console.cloud.google.com/ and create a project.
#   2. APIs & Services > Enable APIs > enable the "Google Drive API".
#   3. APIs & Services > Credentials > Create Credentials > OAuth client ID.
#   4. Application type: "Web application".
#   5. Under "Authorized JavaScript origins" add the URLs the app runs on, e.g.
#        http://localhost:5173
#        https://<your-github-username>.github.io
#   6. Copy the Client ID below.
#
# Then copy this file to `.env` and fill it in.
VITE_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=
